name: Coffee Martini
prepTime: 2 minutes
cookTime: 0 minutes
portions: 1

ingredients:
  - (1.5 oz)	Kahlua
  - (1.5 oz)	Stong Coffee or Espresso
  - (1.5 oz)	Vodka
  - (optional) Heavy Cream
  - (optional) Frangelico
steps:
  - Combine ingredients in shaker
  - Shake with ice until well-chilled
  - Strain into chilled martini glass
  - (optional) Add a splash of Frangelico
  - (optional) Float heavy cream on top
